      <title>探讨 Service Mesh 中一种更高效的代理模式</title>
      <link>https://cloudnativecn.com/blog/a-new-more-efficient-proxy-model/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Jul 2018 12:33:23 +0800</pubDate>
